Plot of Existing Counties and Regions

  • Counties located on the right side of the plot has more disparate outcomes across race and ethnic groups than those on the left side.

Plot of Expanded Regions

  • Counties located on the right side of the plot has more disparate outcomes across race and ethnic groups than those on the left side.

Plot of Existing + Expanded Regions: Version 1

  • Counties located on the right side of the plot has more disparate outcomes across race and ethnic groups than those on the left side.

  • The color of the county indicates whether it is a current HPI County or a proposed new HPI county.

Plot of Existing + Expanded Regions: Version 2

  • Counties located on the right side of the plot has more disparate outcomes across race and ethnic groups than those on the left side.

  • The shape of the county (circle or square) indicates whether it is a current HPI County or a proposed new HPI county.
